title: Future & The Weeknd Tease Video Filmed In Toronto Subway Car
text:
Home > Music > Future & The Weeknd Tease Video Filmed In Toronto Subway Car Future & The Weeknd Tease Video Filmed In Toronto Subway Car 0 0 Posted by Trevor Smith , Mar 22, 2017 at 04:16pm The "Coming Out Strong" video will find Future and The Weeknd riding the TTC. 
Anyone who's taken the TTC in Toronto will recognize the setting of The Weeknd and Future's upcoming video. Both artists have shared posts that show them posted up in a subway car with red faux-velvet seats, a sight anyone who's spent time in Abel's hometown knows far too well. 
While the two have not shared all too much information regarding the shoot, Future captioned his photo as "Still Coming Out Strong," making it seem quite likely the setup is for the HNDRXX collab "Coming Out Strong."Check out the photos below. Watch Future and The Weeknd's video for "Low Life" here .
